[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/qqor/aixcc/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mmongoose[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-v [0m[35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp8mskaimm[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is an AddressSanitizer–detected heap-buffer-overflow in the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction `rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnet_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when processing fuzz-generated packet data. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA patch was proposed that:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Introduces a `header_len` check against `pkt->raw.len` to early‐exit if the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket is too short.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Renames and recalculates header and payload lengths using `[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and `[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Adjusts the computation of `payload_space` and clamps `pkt->pay.len` accordingly.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the same heap-buffer-overflow error recurred at the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39midentical source location and with the same memory layout in subsequent fuzz runs, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the patch did not eliminate the out‐of‐bounds read.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Fuzzer execution triggers a one‐byte read beyond the end of a heap‐allocated [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregion inside `rx_icmp`.  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - ASan report pinpoints the overflow at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m of `src/net_builtin.c` when [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maccessing `pkt->pay.len` or related packet fields.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The packet buffer is [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m bytes long; the code reads at offset [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[39m‐based[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, one[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte past the buffer.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The offending call chain is: `rx_icmp → mg_tcpip_rx → LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput →[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer loop…`[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key Observations in the Initial Log  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash location and stack trace are consistent across runs.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `pkt` is allocated by the fuzzer harness via `malloc` in [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Shadow bytes indicate the access is exactly one byte past the end of a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m‐byte[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mregion.  [0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No prior bounds check on raw packet length before indexing into packet fields.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The patch redefines the start of `rx_icmp` as:[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     static void [0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct mg_tcpip_if *ifp, struct pkt *pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t header_len = [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->raw.len < header_len[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m …[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t payload_space = pkt->raw.len - header_len;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         size_t plen = pkt->pay.len;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mplen > payload_space[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m plen = payload_space;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         …[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This change adds an early exit when the total raw packet length is less than [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe combined size of Ethernet, IP, and ICMP headers.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - It also standardizes header size calculations using dereferenced pointer [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtypes.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Post-Patch Result  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Fuzzing after applying the patch immediately reproduces the same [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐buffer‐overflow.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash site remains `rx_icmp` at net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[39m, reading at offset [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The allocation and address details in the ASan report are unchanged, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the new guard is not preventing the out‐of‐bounds read.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The definitions and contents of `struct pkt`, especially `raw.len`, `pay.len`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand how packet data is laid out in memory.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - How `pkt->raw` and `pkt->pay` lengths are initialized in the fuzzer harness [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`test/fuzz.[0m[1;92mc:95[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m106[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other code paths in `mg_tcpip_rx` or related setup that may mutate packet [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointers or lengths before `rx_icmp`.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The logic in `[0m[1;35mtx_ip[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and subsequent writes to ensure no assumptions about [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket size lead to improper accesses.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any additional fields [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike optional IP options[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that could affect header size[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeyond fixed struct sizes.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m---  [0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis report captures the observed overflow, the attempted patch with its logging [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetails, and highlights code areas requiring deeper review to understand why the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverflow persists. No root-cause speculation or corrective solutions are offered [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhere.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer run triggered an AddressSanitizer heap-buffer-overflow in the function [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min `src/net_builtin.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when reading the ICMP header byte. A patch was [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplied to add length checks and to guard access to the ICMP header based on the IP[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader length field [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`vhl`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. After rebuilding and rerunning the fuzzer, the same [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow at the same source location reoccurred.[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A libFuzzer-driven test exercised `[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmg_tcpip_if*, pkt*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, leading to a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone-byte heap-buffer-overflow on a buffer allocated by `malloc` in the fuzz [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mharness.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash stack trace pinpoints the read access to `pkt->icmp->type` at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `net_builtin.c`.  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The faulty address lies exactly at the boundary of a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte heap buffer, which [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicates that the ICMP header pointer is computed or assumed to be inside a larger[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer than was actually allocated.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImportant Observations  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer log shows no prior checks that packet length is sufficient before [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindexing into the ICMP header.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow occurs on very small or malformed packets [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m34[0m[39m bytes or less[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msuggesting insufficient sanity checking on packet size and header lengths.  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The crash reproduces deterministically under the fuzz harness.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch rewrites `rx_icmp` as follows:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Compute a minimum header length `hlen = [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->ip->vhl & [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m0x0F[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Early return if `pkt->raw.len < hlen` or `pkt->ip == NULL`.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Recompute the ICMP header pointer using `vhl`:  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       `struct icmp *icmph = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp *[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39muint8_t *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->ip + [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->ip->vhl & [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m0x0F[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Inspect `icmph->type` only after these checks.  [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The diff context around line [0m[1;36m379[0m[39m of `src/net_builtin.c`:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```diff[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   static void [0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct mg_tcpip_if *ifp, struct pkt *pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m original code read pkt->icmp->type unguarded[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    [0m[35m/[0m[39m* guard: need Ethernet + IP + ICMP headers before access *[0m[35m/[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    size_t hlen = [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt->eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m +[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                  [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39msize_t[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->ip->vhl & [0m[1;36m0x0F[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m +[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                  [0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->raw.len < hlen || pkt->ip == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    struct icmp *icmph = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp *[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39muint8_t *[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mpkt->ip +[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+                                        [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt->ip->vhl & [0m[1;36m0x0F[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m * [0m[1;36m4[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m+    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39micmph->type != [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m || pkt->ip->dst != ifp->ip[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return;[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     size_t space = ifp->tx.len - hlen, plen = pkt->pay.len;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[33m...[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The same AddressSanitizer error persists at the same location [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating the guard was ineffective for the fuzzer input[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat triggers the overflow.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflowing address remains exactly at the buffer’s boundary, and ASan still [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreports a one-byte read past the allocated region.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This suggests that either:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • The computed `hlen` does not match the actual allocated region for certain [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket variants, or  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • There are other code paths accessing the ICMP header without the new guard in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mplace.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Packet Length Tracking  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Verify that `pkt->raw.len` accurately represents the entire raw packet size, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincluding Ethernet, IP, and ICMP headers plus payload.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Examine how `pkt->raw.len`, `pkt->pay.len`, `pkt->ip`, `pkt->icmp`, and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pkt->eth` are initialized in the higher layers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., in the fuzz harness or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`mg_tcpip_rx`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Header Pointer Computation  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Inspect all uses of `pkt->icmp` and any other ad hoc pointer arithmetic on [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket buffers.  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure the IP header length field [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`vhl`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is validated to be at least the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mminimum [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `vhl >= [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m before multiplying and adding offsets.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Conditional Execution Paths  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm that the patched code path [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwith the new guard[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is always reached for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mICMP packets. There could be alternative branches in `mg_tcpip_rx` or in the code [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath leading to `rx_icmp`.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Buffer Allocation Sites  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Review the code that allocates the packet buffer in `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand in any helper functions to check for off-by-one or underestimated buffer sizes.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Related Protocol Handlers  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - As `rx_icmp` is one of several handlers under `mg_tcpip_rx`, other protocol [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandlers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTCP, UDP[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m may suffer from similar missing-length checks. A broader audit [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof all packet-processing functions is advisable.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mA libFuzzer run on the Mongoose code triggered an AddressSanitizer [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow in the function `rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnet_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The failing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mread is one byte past the end of a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte allocation, as shown by ASan. In [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresponse, a patch was proposed that adds a sequence of boundary checks before any [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mICMP header access—verifying presence of an IP header, computing and validating the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mactual IP header length, confirming the buffer is large enough for Ethernet + IP + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mICMP, and rechecking the ICMP header pointer. After applying the patch, the same [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone-byte heap overflow is still reported at the exact location in `rx_icmp`, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the guard logic did not cover the failing case.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During fuzz testing with libFuzzer, `rx_icmp` is invoked in `mg_tcpip_rx`, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleading to a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte read just past a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte heap allocation.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- ASan report pinpoints the failure at line [0m[1;36m385[0m[39m of `net_builtin.c` in [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmg_tcpip_if*, pkt*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stack trace: `rx_icmp` → `mg_tcpip_rx` → `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` → Fuzzer loop. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The offending address [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0x5040[0m[39m…[0m[1;36m172[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is exactly one byte beyond the [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte region [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m…[0m[1;36m150[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m…[0m[1;36m172[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, indicating insufficient length checks before accessing [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pkt->icmp->type`.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The patch rewrites `rx_icmp` as follows:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Early return if `pkt->ip` is NULL.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Extract and validate the IP header length [0m[1;39m([0m[39mminimum [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m words[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Compute the combined minimum length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*eth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + ip_hdr_len + [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mstruct icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Return if `pkt->raw.len` is less than this combined header size.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Compute `icmph` pointer by offsetting from `pkt->ip`.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Return if the ICMP header would run past the end of the packet buffer.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Only then check `icmph->type` and `pkt->ip->dst` and proceed with echo reply [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Key insertions: checks on `pkt->raw.len`, explicit pointer arithmetic using [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`vhl`, and bounds guard for the ICMP header.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPost-Patch Result  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Fuzzer run log remains largely the same, with the crash still at [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[35m/src/mongoose/src/[0m[95mnet_builtin.c[0m[39m:[0m[1;92m385:18[0m[39m in rx_icmp`, and ASan complaining of a read[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mjust beyond the allocated region.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The reported offset and allocation details are identical, demonstrating the guard[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic did not intercept the malformed input case.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The relationship between `pkt->raw.len`, `pkt->pay.len`, and the memory region [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbacking the packet buffer. The patch checks `raw.len` but the overflow might [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvolve other fields like `pkt->pay` or `pkt->icmp` pointers.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definition and management of `struct pkt`, especially how `raw`, `eth`, `ip`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`icmp`, and `pay` are laid out in memory and populated by `mg_tcpip_rx`.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The incoming packet parsing logic in `mg_tcpip_rx` to see if `pkt->ip`, [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pkt->pay.len`, or `pkt->raw.len` are set in a way that misrepresents the true [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer size.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The construction of transmit buffer `ifp->tx.len` and how `hlen` and `space` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minteract with actual packet data.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Other code paths in `net_builtin.c` that compute header lengths or manipulate [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpacket buffers, to ensure consistent bounds checks across all protocols.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m-v [0m[35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmp8mskaimm[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer run against the Mongoose codebase triggered an AddressSanitizer error: a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow in the function `rx_icmp` called from `mg_tcpip_rx`. An [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mattempted patch in `src/net_builtin.c` added an ICMP‐specific branch and a [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreliminary length check before invoking `rx_icmp`. However, re-running the harness[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith the patch applied produced the same heap-buffer-overflow at the identical [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msource location, indicating the patch did not prevent the out‐of‐bounds read.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- During fuzzing [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, AddressSanitizer reported a [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow in `[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmg_tcpip_if*, pkt*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m[39m.  [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The overflow occurs immediately after a [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m-byte allocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mheap left redzone[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith the corrupted access address being exactly one byte past the allocated region.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Stack trace: `rx_icmp` ← `mg_tcpip_rx` ← `LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput` ← fuzzer [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mruntime.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The packet [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`pkt.raw`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was allocated by the fuzz harness; the ICMP handler reads [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeyond the buffer.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Modified `src/net_builtin.c` around line [0m[1;36m882[0m[39m:  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Introduced an `else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpkt.ip->proto == IPPROTO_ICMP[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` branch.  [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Added a check that `pkt.raw.len` is at least enough to cover Ethernet, IP [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheader [0m[1;39m([0m[39musing `ihl`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and ICMP header [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35msizeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pkt.icmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Set `pkt.icmp` pointer before calling `[0m[1;35mrx_icmp[0m[1;39m([0m[39mifp, &pkt[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Removed original IP‐length‐based truncation logic in this branch, isolating ICMP [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandling in a guarded block.[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLog After Applying Patch  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The fuzzer run logs are essentially identical: ASan reports the same [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-buffer-overflow at `net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385:18[0m[39m` in `rx_icmp`.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The allocation size, skew of [0m[1;36m34[0m[39m bytes, and access one byte past remain unchanged.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No new checks or branches prevented the overflow; the error persists under the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame conditions.  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of `rx_icmp` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround net_builtin.[0m[1;92mc:385[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and how it reads ICMP [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpayload or fields beyond the header.  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The calculation and use of `pkt.raw.len`, `ihl`, and any subsequent offset [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marithmetic in `mg_tcpip_rx` and `rx_icmp`.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The assumptions made about the minimum packet size in upstream code paths [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEthernet + IP + ICMP[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any interactions between IP header length [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`ihl`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and actual buffer length [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprovided by the fuzzer harness.[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
